org.sensorhub.api.persistence

Interface IBasicStorage<ConfigType extends StorageConfig>

  • Type Parameters:
    ConfigType - Type of storage configuration
    All Superinterfaces:
    IEventProducer, IModule<ConfigType>, IStorageModule<ConfigType>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InMemoryBasicStorage

    public interface IBasicStorage<ConfigType extends StorageConfig>
extends IStorageModule<ConfigType>

    Storage for one or more data streams coming from a single source. (for instance, the source can be a sensor, a service or a process) This also supports storing lineage information if a description of the data source is provided.
